    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rioroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "rioroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "choice_selection",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "他に好きな人はいないと断言する",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01-koh005.wav",
              "text": "何を言ってるんですか\n俺が好きなのは莉央さんだけです\n他に好きな人なんていません",
              "startTime": 104.300001462,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "なぜそう思うのか尋ねる",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01-koh006.wav",
              "text": "他に好きな人だなんて……\nどうしてそう思ったんですか？\n理由を教えて下さい",
              "startTime": 110.8666681287,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "choice_selection",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "分かりました。別れましょう",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tears-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 374.1333968474
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01-rio027.wav",
              "text": "{user}君のことが好きよ\nだから、私よりももっと\n貴方にふさわしい人と幸せになってね",
              "startTime": 374.1333968474,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "嫌だ。絶対に別れません",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_heart-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 384.5000635141
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01-rio028.wav",
              "text": "そうよね\n本当は私も、別れたくなんかない……",
              "startTime": 384.5000635141,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01-rio029.wav",
              "text": "これからも沢山迷惑を掛けると思う\nすれ違うこともあるかもしれない\nそれでも……ずっとそばにいてくれる？",
              "startTime": 390.5334029509,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01-koh020.wav",
              "text": "はい\n俺はいつまでも莉央さんのそばにいます",
              "startTime": 401.5334029509,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01-rio030.wav",
              "text": "ありがとう。貴方の言葉を信じるわ\n好きよ\nいつまでも、私のそばにいてね",
              "startTime": 406.3667362843,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01-rio001.wav",
      "text": "はぁ……ただいま……",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01-koh001.wav",
      "text": "お帰りなさい。残業お疲れ様です\n莉央さん、お風呂にしますか？\nご飯にしますか？　それとも……",
      "startTime": 3.5333330791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rioroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "rioroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 11.1666668575
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01-rio002.wav",
      "text": "ごめんなさい\nまだ仕事が残ってるから\n私は部屋で仕事の続きをするわ",
      "startTime": 11.1666668575,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rioroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "rioroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 17.4000001908
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01-koh002.wav",
      "text": "そうですか……\n仕事も大事ですが、健康第一ですから\nあまり無理はしないで下さい",
      "startTime": 17.4000001908,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "stop",
      "startTime": 24.3800000191
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rioroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "rioroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 25.0666668575
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01-rio003.wav",
      "text": "無理するなですって……？\n無理するに決まってるでしょ！　社運を\n懸けたプロジェクトを私は任されたのよ！",
      "startTime": 25.0666668575,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rioroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "rioroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 33.6333347957
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_serious-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 33.6333347957
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01-rio004.wav",
      "text": "入社一年目の貴方に\nこの重圧は分からないでしょうね\n私がどれだけ周囲から期待されているか……",
      "startTime": 33.6333347957,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01-rio005.wav",
      "text": "言われたことだけやっていれば\n評価されるような人に\n私が感じている責任の重みなんて……",
      "startTime": 41.2000014623,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rioroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "rioroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 47.4666660945
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01-rio006.wav",
      "text": "あ……ごめんなさい……\n今のは本気で言った訳じゃないの\nイライラして、つい……",
      "startTime": 47.4666660945,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rioroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "rioroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 56.0999994278
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01-koh003.wav",
      "text": "気にしてませんよ\n毎日こんなに忙しかったら\nイライラする時だってありますよね",
      "startTime": 56.0999994278,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01-rio007.wav",
      "text": "……貴方っていつもそう\n私が仕事を優先して約束を破っても……\nイライラしてかんしゃくを起こしても……",
      "startTime": 62.2000040053,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rioroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "rioroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 71.1666676202
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01-rio008.wav",
      "text": "文句一つ言わずに、いつも優しく\n受け止めてくれて……\n悪いのはいつだって私なのに……",
      "startTime": 71.1666676202,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01-rio009.wav",
      "text": "{user}君に\n何度も嫌な思いをさせて……\n私は恋人失格だわ……",
      "startTime": 80.9666681287,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rioroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "rioroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 88.8000034966
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01-koh004.wav",
      "text": "恋人失格だなんて、そんなことありません\nどうしてそんなことを言うんですか",
      "startTime": 88.8000034966,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rioroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "rioroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 95.533335304
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01-rio010.wav",
      "text": "だって、貴方はもう私のことなんて\n好きじゃないでしょ？\n他に好きな人が出来たんでしょ？",
      "startTime": 95.533335304,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "stop",
      "startTime": 102.4002508161
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rioroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "rioroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 117.300001462
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 117.300001462
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01-rio011.wav",
      "text": "……私、見たのよ\n{user}君が瑠依と\n親密そうにしているところを",
      "startTime": 117.300001462,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01-rio012.wav",
      "text": "凄く仲が良さそうで、二人はお似合いだと\n思ったわ。私よりも瑠依のような子の方が\n貴方を幸せに出来るんだと思った……",
      "startTime": 124.2333347954,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rioroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "rioroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 136.800001462
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01-koh007.wav",
      "text": "考え過ぎですよ\n俺の恋人は莉央さんで瑠依はただの友達です",
      "startTime": 136.800001462,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rioroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "rioroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 142.700001462
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01-rio013.wav",
      "text": "……ごめんなさい。そうよね……私は何を\n言っているのかしら。こんなこと言うなんて\n……私は貴方の優しさに甘え過ぎてるわね",
      "startTime": 142.700001462,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 22366.663932900025
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rioroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "rioroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 156.8666660942
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01-rio014.wav",
      "text": "ごめんなさい……\n悪いけど、私は部屋で仕事をするから\nしばらく一人にしてちょうだい",
      "startTime": 156.8666660942,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rioroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "rioroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 167.3333195366
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_07_01-koh008.wav",
      "text": "（違うよ、莉央さん\n俺は優しくなんかない\n俺は臆病なだけだ）",
